{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7d22c1b42","title":"毛泽东视察四川省一个养猪场时的谈话","origin":"《中国妇女》1958年第7期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1126be102a","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"f7d22c1b42"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0d42c13787","type":"title","text":"毛泽东视察四川省一个养猪场时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"7129b14ff7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：（对饲养员）辛苦了，好同志！（握手）祝你们获得更大成功！","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"698d853cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：全靠你老人家的教导！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"ff4cfaaabc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：主要是你们自己的努力。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"401271710d","type":"paragraph","text":"（对社长）能使你们全社妇女都当上模范吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"659d0e7c91","type":"paragraph","text":"社长：保证全能当上，毛主席！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"688efe2c43","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：全当上模范未必得行吧！只能在二、三年内做到有一半妇女当上模范就不错了。你说我这个看法保守吗？（众笑）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"ddd91ed65c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：参观一下你们的养猪场好吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"b8beb86f29","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：欢迎，欢迎！毛主席多指教！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"1e5f6d1744","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：别什么都要我指教吧，我和××都是来向你们学习的，在许多事情上，你们比我们内行多了，是吧？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"785bd3938b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：这是什么？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"33ee4986ed","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：是糖化牛粪，拿来喂猪的，猪很爱吃。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"ad424bf9f1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：真是新鲜事儿，牛粪也能喂猪！怎么个制法，介绍一下吧，（摸出日记本来作记录，向××说）来，我们都记上吧，这是群众的创造！从前我们就没听见说过。看来我们中国那句老话：“做到老，学到老”实在不错！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"a172d6e46f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：（对一个回乡知识青年）回家喂猪有意见吗？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"83a9c7b2f1","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：有啥意见呀！我一辈子也不愿意离开这养猪场哩！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"a4d11e50f7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：很好！可要把你学的科学，传授给群众才更好。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"4e78eba59b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：……多看看先进的东西，眼光就会更开阔些。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"33ba1c23e1","type":"paragraph","text":"（亲自给一头猪打了蛋清针，然后对××说）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"b2ceec85d4","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的经验真不少，特别是代饲料，如果全国都推广，一年要节约好几十亿斤粮食哩！请记者同志在报纸上介绍一下好吗？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"4413ab6a5b","type":"paragraph","text":"×××：办得到。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"ed9457720c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：最好后天见报。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"3c80993455","type":"paragraph","text":"（对饲养员）谢谢你们！对我们教育太大了！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"90d564c750","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：可有人看不起我们哩！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"75af343d45","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：谁？谁是顽固派？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"f04f13f0de","type":"paragraph","text":"（饲养员介绍一些人如何从轻视妇女到称赞妇女的成绩。）","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"},{"id":"9a87058b96","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：看不起妇女的人虽不多，但哪里总有几个，这不完全怪他们，过去封建制度对他们影响太深了，脑筋一下不容易转过弯来，又不能用飞机大炮来对付他们。那怎么办呢？我看除了加强教育外，最好的办法，就是妇女同志们做出成绩来，多拿事实给他们看，看得多了，他们脑子里的那个封建王国就会不攻自破的。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42"}],"page":{"id":"b2a4d5b072","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f7d22c1b42","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}